title: Pack 3 Medicine Cabinet Replacement Shelves - (Black) (13.5 inch)

Effortlessly organize your toiletries, medications, and other essentials with these sturdy and stylish shelves. Whether you're renovating or simply refreshing your existing cabinet, these replacement shelves are a must-have for a tidy and functional bathroom.
